<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>SafeVoice | Women Safety</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">SafeVoice</div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a onclick="showSection('home')">Home</a></li>
        <li><a onclick="showSection('about')">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a onclick="showSection('services')">Services</a></li>
        <li><a onclick="showSection('qa')">Q & A</a></li>

        <li class="dropdown">
            <a>Login <i class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></a>
            <div class="dropdown-menu">
                <a href="/login/user">User Login</a>
                <a href="/login/admin">Admin Login</a>
                <a href="/login/resolver">Resolver Login</a>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</nav>


<main class="content-wrapper">

    <section id="home" class="section active">
        <h1>Empowering Women.<br>Ensuring Safety.</h1>
        <p>
            SafeVoice is a secure platform where women can report safety issues
            and receive professional guidance from trusted authorities.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="section">
        <h2>About SafeVoice</h2>
        <p>
            SafeVoice bridges the gap between women and support systems.
            Every issue is handled with privacy, empathy, and responsibility.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="section">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>

        <div class="card-container">
            <div class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i>Harassment Cases </div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney"></i>Domestic Violence Cases</div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i>Cyber Crime Cases</div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i>Legal Guidance from authorized resolver</div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>Counseling</div>
            <div class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone-volume"></i>Emergency Help</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="qa" class="section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <details class="faq">
            <summary>Is SafeVoice confidential?</summary>
            <p>Yes, SafeVoice ensures 100% confidentiality and privacy.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
            <summary>Can I report anonymously?</summary>
            <p>Yes, anonymous reporting is fully supported.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
            <summary>Who resolves issues?</summary>
            <p>Issues are handled by verified NGOs, legal advisors, and counselors.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
            <summary>Is SafeVoice free to use?</summary>
            <p>Yes, SafeVoice is completely free for all users.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
            <summary>Is cyber crime supported?</summary>
            <p>Yes, cyber crime cases are handled with expert guidance.</p>
        </details>
    </section>

</main>

<footer>
    <p>Â© 2025 SafeVoice | Emergency: 112 | Women Helpline: 181</p>
</footer>

<script>
function showSection(id) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach(sec => {
        sec.classList.remove('active');
    });
    document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
